data.description: The home is a split level with a open floor plan that is perfect for entertaining. This home was recently renovated with New roof, New HVAC, New Kitchen with Granite Countertops, New Windows, New LVP Floors, New Water Heater and crawl space encapsulated. Kitchen overlooks private back yard that is perfect for those fall bonfires. The basement is finished with a bedroom and a bonus room. The upstairs features 3 bedrooms that are spacious. The primary suite has an en-suite bathroom. The home is close to shopping and restaurants and easy access to I-20. The home is being sold as-is
